{"type": "article", "id": 17319, "title": "装泡沫的沙漏", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-10T06:20:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 129, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135528otsGW8OkcH14M6YU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自日本设计师 Norihiko Terayama 的沙漏，但他在瓶子里放进去的是泡沫而不是沙子。当气泡从上滑落，令人感到的是浪漫的瞬间而不是时光逝去的伤感，这就是设计师想表达的把握当下的思想。沙漏的大小两种型号有不同的流动速度，分别高 15 厘米和 9 厘米，售价 55 美元和 38 美元。<a href=\"http://shop.spoon-tamago.com/collections/new/products/awaglass-an-hourglass-filled-with-bubbles\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。 </a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144415WGlMkHhKdXN9uvsV.gif\" width=\"448\" height=\"251\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56026786\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144418D5EmGp9yVRndcCwQ.jpg\" width=\"709\" height=\"485\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68406206\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144419cies8yq5DkVfh3L7.jpg\" width=\"709\" height=\"474\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66854725\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144421IFdw6iRgM8pQ0BZ4.jpg\" width=\"709\" height=\"1061\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49647391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}